HEADWORD: Alehoof
<hw>Ale"hoof`</hw> <pr>(⟦amac⟧l"h⟦oomac⟧f`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[AS. <ets>h⟦omac⟧fe</ets> ground ivy; the first part is perh. a
corruption: cf. OE. <ets>heyhowe</ets> hedgehove, ground ivy, ⟦ldquo⟧in
old MSS. <ets>heyhowe</ets>, <ets>heyoue</ets>, <ets>haihoue</ets>,
<ets>halehoue</ets>.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Prior</au>.]</ety> <def>Ground ivy
(<spn>Nepeta Glechoma</spn>).</def>⟦br⟧
